images.name: Josh Allen ices the game with incredible rushing TD on 4th down
images.caption: Josh Allen comes up with a clutch 26-yard touchdown to give the Bills a two-score lead over the Chiefs late in the fourth quarter.

articles.description: — After watching quarterback Josh Allen bounce off two Kansas City Chiefs defenders before crossing the goal line on a 26-yard run, Bills receiver Khalil Shakir joined the rest of the packed...
articles.headline: Josh Allen seals Bills' 30-21 win over Chiefs with TD run, ending bid for perfect season

articles.description: The defense and QB Justin Herbert buoyed the Chargers as they avoided another late-game meltdown to beat the Bengals on Sunday night, a scenario that illustrated how different the team is under coach Jim Harbaugh.
articles.headline: Chargers shake Bengals late, note difference under Jim Harbaugh

images.name: Chargers win as J.K. Dobbins tumbles into end zone in closing seconds
images.caption: The Chargers hand the Bengals a crushing defeat as J.K. Dobbins takes off for the clutch touchdown late in the fourth quarter.

articles.description: — Jim Harbaugh and the Los Angeles Chargers finally have their signature win.
articles.headline: Chargers beat Bengals 34-27 on Dobbins' late TD after squandering 21-point lead

articles.description: In what has been a familiar sight this season, the Bengals saw a potential win slip away Sunday night against the Chargers. Ja'Marr Chase was among those left searching for an answer to the team's inability to finish games but did offer a starting point.
articles.headline: Ja'Marr Chase, Bengals short on answers after latest close loss
